text: Kazuhiro Tanaka is a modern pentathlete from Japan. Kazuhiro competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics. He was born on July 8, 1936.Kazuhiro Tanaka == References == Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese modern pentathletes Category:Olympians for Japan Category:Sportspeople from Fukuoka Prefecture
